 And so if you assume that at any given time,

11:04.700 --> 11:06.660
 somebody might have trillions of virus in them

11:06.660 --> 11:07.980
 and any given individual,

11:07.980 --> 11:10.620
 so then multiply trillions by millions

11:10.620 --> 11:12.980
 and you get a lot of viruses out there.

