 We have millions of these tests.

13:48.540 --> 13:51.820
 These tests are simple paper strip tests.

13:51.820 --> 13:54.660
 They are, inside of this thing

13:54.660 --> 13:56.440
 is just a little piece of paper.

13:58.000 --> 14:00.340
 Now I can actually open it up here.

14:00.340 --> 14:01.540
 There we go.

