 And I hate to be the Debbie Downer here,

1:00:09.420 --> 1:00:13.540
 but there's a lot of unknowns with this vaccine.

1:00:13.540 --> 1:00:14.620
 You've already mentioned one,

1:00:14.620 --> 1:00:16.100
